// Regression: decisions with back-edges (retry/yes-to-done) should exit
// from E/W tips, not N/S. Conditions stored with capital letters ('Yes', 'No')
// from single-quote syntax must be matched case-insensitively.

#start Start
Review CCTV footage.

#decision Is there a security incident?
  -> 'Yes' Call Police
  -> 'No' Document

Call Police
Observe until police arrive

#decision Police arrived?
  -> 'Yes' Monitor until resolved.
  -> 'No' Observe until police arrive

Monitor until resolved.

#decision Resolved?
  -> 'Yes' #end Done
  -> 'No' Monitor until resolved.

Document -> #end Done
